trans-unit.source: Azure AD Graph Error Codes
trans-unit.target: Azure AD Graph Error Codes

trans-unit.source: This topic lists Azure AD Graph error codes, error messages, and actions to consider when correcting errors.
trans-unit.target: This topic lists Azure AD Graph error codes, error messages, and actions to consider when correcting errors.

trans-unit.source: In general, HTTP 500-series errors respond to retries, preferably distributed over increasingly long time intervals ("retry with a back-off interval") and with a random distribution factor.
trans-unit.target: In general, HTTP 500-series errors respond to retries, preferably distributed over increasingly long time intervals ("retry with a back-off interval") and with a random distribution factor.

trans-unit.source: However, 400-series errors indicate a problem that must be fixed before retrying.
trans-unit.target: However, 400-series errors indicate a problem that must be fixed before retrying.
